DLMtool 5.1.999

What management procedures need what data

Required.Rd

A function that finds all the MPs and searches the function text for slots in the Data object

Required(funcs = NA)

Arguments

funcs

A character vector of management procedures

Value

A matrix of MPs and their required data in terms of Data slotnames

See also

Can Cant Needed MPtype Data

Examples

Required(c("DCAC", "AvC"))
#>      [,1]  
#> [1,] "DCAC"
#> [2,] "AvC" 
#>      [,2]                                                                      
#> [1,] "t, AvC, Dt, Mort, FMSY_M, BMSY_B0, CV_Dt, CV_Mort, CV_FMSY_M, CV_BMSY_B0"
#> [2,] "Year, Cat, Units, LHYear"
